---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout>
  <div
    class="mt-4 border p-4 rounded-md shadow flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4"
  >
    <img
      class="h-64 w-52 rounded-md shadow-md object-cover hover:opacity-75 transition duration-500 ease-in-out transform hover:border-2 hover:border-gray-300 border-2 border-white"
      src="/novelimg.JPEG"
      alt="placeholder"
    /><div>
      <div class="cursor-pointer hover:underline transition-all ease-in-out">
        <a class="font-bold text-xl">Nine Star Hegemon Body Art</a>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <div class="text-green-500 uppercase">
          <p><span class="mr-1 text-lg">#</span>Action</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-green-500 uppercase">
          <p><span class="mr-1 text-lg">#</span>adventure</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-2 text-yellow-500">
        <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
        <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
        <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
        <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
        <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
        (4.5)
      </div>
      <div class="mt-2 mb-8">
        In the tens of thousands of great worlds,Mu Yun, reincarnated into the
        body of an illegitimate son who had been bullied and humiliated. Lorem
        ipsum dolor sit, amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Facere ipsam
        cupiditate, necessitatibus numquam enim consectetur ab itaque ad
        officia. Illum reprehenderit ut laboriosam corrupti perspiciatis,
        similique pariatur nesciunt debitis et?
      </div>

      <div class="flex justify-start gap-4">
        <a
          href="/reader"
          class="inline-flex items-center uppercase font-bold bg-green-500 text-white border-0 py-1 px-3 focus:outline-none hover:bg-green-700 rounded text-base mt-4 md:mt-0"
          >Read now
        </a><button
          class="inline-flex items-center uppercase font-bold bg-green-500 text-white border-0 py-1 px-3 focus:outline-none hover:bg-green-700 rounded text-base mt-4 md:mt-0"
          ><i class="bi bi-bookmark-fill mr-2"></i>Bookmark
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
